PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry, Science and Technology of Patrick J. Lavelle, of Toronto, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Federal Business Development Bank to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years; and designation of Patrick J. Lavelle as Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Federal Business Development Bank to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective September 27, 1994, in the place of Bertrand J. Lavoie, whose term has expired.
